"><span begin="0:27.301" end="0:27.671">針</span><span begin="0:27.671" end="0:28.799">でもなんでも</span> <span begin="0:28.799" end="0:28.988">飲</span><span begin="0:28.988" end="0:29.557">ませて</span><span begin="0:29.557" end="0:30.315">いただき</span> <span begin="0:30.315" end="0:30.784">Mon</span><span begin="0:30.784" end="0:31.594">day</span></p><p begin="0:32.096" end="0:34.835" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:32.096" end="0:32.296">It</span> <span begin="0:32.296" end="0:32.665">doesn't</span> <span begin="0:32.665" end="0:33.049">matter</span> <span begin="0:33.049" end="0:33.251">if</span> <span begin="0:33.251" end="0:33.465">it's</span> <span begin="0:33.465" end="0:33.835">Sun</span><span begin="0:33.835" end="0:34.835">day</span></p><p begin="0:36.418" end="0:39.394" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:36.418" end="0:37.032">鏡</span><span begin="0:37.032" end="0:37.164">よ</span><span begin="0:37.164" end="0:37.776">鏡</span><span begin="0:37.776" end="0:37.945">よ</span> <span begin="0:37.945" end="0:38.292">この</span><span begin="0:38.292" end="0:38.466">世</span><span begin="0:38.466" end="0:38.639">で</span><span begin="0:38.639" end="0:39.394">1番</span></p><p begin="0:39.404" end="0:43.645" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:39.404" end="0:39.605">変</span><span begin="0:39.605" end="0:40.412">わること</span><span begin="0:40.412" end="0:40.955">のない</span> <span begin="0:40.955" end="0:41.360">愛</span><span begin="0:41.360" end="0:41.627">を</span><span begin="0:41.627" end="0:42.125">くれる</span><span begin="0:42.125" end="0:42.491">のは</span> <span begin="0:42.491" end="0:42.887">だ</span><span begin="0:42.887" end="0:43.645">れ</span></p><p begin="0:44.124" end="0:47.375" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="0:44.124" end="0:44.512">No</span> <span begin="0:44.512" end="0:44.658">need</span> <span begin="0:44.658" end="0:44.758">to</span> <span begin="0:44.758" end="0:45.028">ask</span> <span begin="0:45.028" end="0:45.224">cause